      "actionStep": "Read back through the four stories and notice which one most resembles your own situation, whether in the nature of the struggle or in how stuck you've felt. Then ask what that person did differently from what you're currently doing—did they finally stop holding back during the practice, commit to it daily over months rather than occasionally, or keep going after an initial setback? Identify the one specific difference that seems most relevant to you right now."
